	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Go to the Colony Barracks with &quot;goto 728 16 14&quot;&#xD;&#xA;- Let the Mistress of Souls finish blessing the Skull Lashers. Do not come too close or interfere.&#xD;&#xA;- Talk to Krustine, Mistress of Souls, after the blessing AD has finished.&#xD;&#xA;- If you attacked Ketheric on the Moonrise rooftop before coming to Colony, the Myrkulites will be hostile to you on sight." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="43" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Reaction to interrupting Krustine's blessing ceremony in the Colony Barracks. She is blessing three Skull Lashers, and approaching or interrupting will cause her to interrogate you." />
